this movie is why fairy tales should not be revisited fairy tales are written the way that they are written for a reason . and when greedy producers and actors and directors realize this maybe the world will be a better place . the characters in fairy tales are n't suppose to grow up . they are written for certain age groups and are moral lessons about concequences in life and how she/he 's life will change depending on which choices that one will make and direction she/he follows